      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that will likely need attention in the near future. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches and minor dents. The interior has noticeable wear with some staining and minor damage to the upholstery. Overall, this is a functional vehicle that needs some work.",
